d the English-speaking minority rights battle in Quebec, Voice of the Vanishing Minority makes for timely reading in light of recent developments in Quebec.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Journalism.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978077356725240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780773567252423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780773567252/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles